title: Where Results Stand in Several Undecided Senate and House Races
description: More than two days after polls closed across the United States, control of both houses of Congress is still up for grabs, with many election outcomes not yet determined.
dc:creator: Matt Stevens
media:credit: Mikayla Whitmore for The New York Times
media:description: Senator Catherine Cortez Masto gives remarks at the Nevada Democratic Victory election night party at the Encore in Las Vegas, Nev. on Tuesday, Nov. 8, 2022.
